The paper also introduces a new training technique using a differentiable shape decoder, which involves machine learning, so it could also belong to the cs.LG (Machine Learning) category. Additionally, the paper utilizes Fourier series, which is a mathematical concept, so it could belong to the cs.GR (Graphics) category. The paper also involves image processing, which could place it in the cs.MM (Multimedia) category. Finally, the paper could also belong to the cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) category, as instance segmentation is a subfield of AI.
